    <string name="info">
        At First, thank you for using my App.

        \n\nWith this app you have an overview of your expenses. To add a new issue,
        double-click on the day of the calendar. There you must enter a Title and a Value.

        \n\nIf you want, you can enter a description and edit the color of the title. Then you can save the issue.
        If you have a Repeated issue, go to “ADD REPEATED ISSUES”
        and there you can enter an issue which is repeated every Year, Month, Week or Day. From the Start Date until the end date.

        \n\nIf you want to edit your issue, you just have to click on the issue on the list. There you can edit or delete the issue.

        \n\nIn the Main Menu you can change the Currency by Clicking on the “CHANGE CURRENCY” Button,
        there you have to enter the 3-Letter Code of the Currency.

        \n\nTo have an overview of all your expenses click on “OVERVIEW”.
        There you can choose if it should be sorted by Date or value and if ascending or descending.
        Furthermore, you can choose if it should show a specific year, month or from a start and end day.
        If you want to delete ALL issues click on the button “DELETE ALL”. This will delete all your issues, not only the ones showed.

        \n\nI would like if you rate my app or if you want you can spend some money for the creator.

    </string>

